    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that still turns heads? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in such solid shape! It\u2019s been really well-cared for, runs like a dream, and is totally ready for its next big adventure. If you want a quality vehicle that feels great on the road and has tons of life left in it, you\u2019ve gotta come check this out. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering its signature high-revving linear power through six individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring a visceral connection to the pavement. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's known structural nuances. Performance is bolstered by a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously overhauled for optimal cam timing and low-end torque. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, featuring consistent compression across all cylinders and a smooth-shifting Getrag unit. This is a driver\u2019s machine, balanced perfectly for both spirited canyon carving and high-speed stability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor, honest signs of road use one would expect from a well-loved car\u2014such as a few faint stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is free of rips or stains, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity audio system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule, including a recent comprehensive fluid service, new filters, and a thorough brake inspection. The engine pulls smoothly across the power band, and the transmission shifts with crisp precision. We have kept a detailed log of service records to provide the next owner with complete peace of mind. This is a solid, dependable example of its class, ideal for someone who appreciates a car that has been treated with genuine respect and is ready for the road ahead.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a refined example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure dependable performance and lasting comfort. Featuring a sophisticated interior and a robust powertrain, it offers an exceptional balance of luxury and utility for the discerning driver. Experience the assurance of quality engineering and professional upkeep in this standout offering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me day in and day out. It runs like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-loved. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and the factory M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring mechanical engagement and superb corner-exit traction. The engine's individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response, while the hydraulic-assist steering rack offers the tactile feedback missing from modern EPS units. Critically, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and the throttle actuators have been upgraded, mitigating common S65 failure points. The suspension retains its factory kinematics with no bushing play or subframe fatigue. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is mechanically sound and free of fluid seepage or VANOS noise. This is a high-revving, analog machine for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical provenance over concours aesthetics.",
      "price": 32500.0,
